+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                                                   |
|                                                                                   |
|               Lidy - A small C library for sparse matrices managing               |
|                             (includes libxml2-2.6.26)                             |
|                                                                                   |
|                                                                                   |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+


The goal of this small project, under the LGPL license, is to build a library 
allowing to handle sparse matrices. Furthermore, there isthe possibility to load and 
save these matrices into XML format.

For any extra information on the general working of the project, please consult the 
documentation written in (LaTeX | HTML) format, located in 'doc'.
